CIIS</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></nav><div class="banner-wrap"><div class="wsite-elements wsite-not-footer wsite-header-elements"><div class="wsite-section-wrap"><div class="wsite-section wsite-header-section wsite-section-bg-image" style="height: 165px;background-image: url(&quot;/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/fd96v4bf89rs4.jpg&quot;) ;background-repeat: no-repeat ;/* background-position: 50.00% 30.52% */ ;background-size: 100% ;background-color: transparent ;background-size: cover;"><div class="wsite-section-content"><div class="container"><div class="banner"><div class="wsite-section-elements"><div><div class="wsite-image wsite-image-border-none " style="padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;text-align:inherit"> <a> <img src="/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/6654848654.png" alt="Picture" style="width:352;max-width:100%;width:645px;padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:15px;"> </a><div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="wrap-outer" style="margin-top: 65px;"><div class="wrap-inner"><div class="post soft-double-bottom global-bg container-outer"><div class="container"><div class="row row-fluid equalize" style="display: inline-table; height: 100%; /* box-shadow: 0 0 10px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, .6); */"><div class="col-sm-12 eq bg-white" style="visibility: visible;"><div class="alt-title global-bgcolor-light soft-double" style="display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; padding-top: 30px !important; padding-bottom: 20px !important;"><h3 class="alt-title-head global-color" style="font-weight:bold;">First Advanced Informatics Workshop</h3></div><div class="bg-white soft-double post-body wp-text"><center><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-2925 wiafinal" src="/2019/src/assets/media/misc/wia-final.jpg" alt="" width="70%" height="auto"><br></p></center><p><strong><em>Purpose:</em></strong> The XV promotion of Computer and Systems Engineering of the National University Jorge Basadre Grohmann of Tacna, has the pleasure of inviting the <span style="text-decoration: underline;"> First Advanced Informatics Workshop</span> which is one of the events that will be taking place in the framework of the XX International Congress of Informatics and CIIS 2019 systems.<br> This workshop will be a space for discussion and exchange of research results of various academic authors whether they are: professors, students, graduates or professionals from the region, the country or from other places; for this, they are invited to submit an evaluation of their research papers in short format, being reviewed by a program committee composed of renowned academics from different countries of the world.</p><p><strong>Call for Papers</strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Professors, students, graduates and professional researchers are invited to send their scientific research articles in English or Spanish, these should be sent through the <span style="text-decoration: underline;">EasyChair</span> platform through the link:</p><a href="https://easychair.org/cfp/IWIA-XXCIIS2019" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://easychair.org/cfp/IWIA-XXCIIS2019</a><p style="margin-top: 10px;"> The articles will be reviewed and evaluated by a program committee of international level of which the two best articles selected will be published in the journal Science and Development of the National University Jorge Basadre Grohmann that is indexed in the Latindex network. <br><a href="/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/Formato_ES_IWIA_2019.docx" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #333333; font-weight: normal;">Download the Submission Template (Word) <i class="far fa-file-word-o" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></p><p><strong>Place</strong></p><p>First WIA will be held on the campus of the Jorge Basadre Grohmann National University, Tacna - Peru, which is 1235 km south of Lima, the capital of Peru.</p><h4 style="letter-spacing: 0.05em; background: #fff; border-left: solid #0c0078;">Journal of Advanced Informatics Workshop&nbsp;&nbsp; (2019)&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: #cc0000;">NEW</span></h4><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-2925" src="/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/66c19942ab4ba346fdb64ccc04cde373-3.png?ver=2.0.0" alt="" width="202" height="286"><br> <a href="/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/POSTER_IWIA_2019_EN.pdf?ver=2.0.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download the complete journal <i class="far fa-file-pdf"></i></a></p><p><strong>Topics of interest</strong></p><p>First WIA will receive various short-term research papers from the different branches of information and technology, some of the topics are:</p><ul style="padding-left: 30px;"><li>Software Engineering</li><li>Data and knowledge engineering</li><li>Robotics and automation</li><li>Intelligent Systems</li><li>Emerging technologies</li><li>New trends in computing</li></ul><p><strong>Important dates</strong></p><ul style="padding-left: 30px;"><li>Shipment Opening 【June 5, 2019】</li><li style="text-decoration: line-through;">Submission Deadline 【September 16, 2019】</li><li style="text-decoration: line-through;">Author Notification 【September 27, 2019】</li><li style="text-decoration: line-through;">Camera Ready 【October 4, 2019】</li><br><li style="text-decoration: line-through;">Submission Deadline 【September 23, 2019】</li><li style="text-decoration: line-through;">Author Notification 【October 11, 2019】</li><li style="text-decoration: line-through;">Camera Ready 【October 18, 2019】</li><li> Presentation 【November 12, 2019】</li></ul><p><strong>Organizing Committee</strong></p><ul style="padding-left: 30px;"><li>MSc. Edgar Taya Acosta, Jorge Basadre Grohmann University, Peru</li><li>MSc. Arnold C. Loaiza Fabian, Jorge Basadre Grohmann University, Peru</li><li>Dalthon Mamani Hualpa, Jorge Basadre Grohmann University, Peru</li></ul><p><strong>I WIA PROGRAM COMMITTEE</strong></p><ul style="padding-left: 30px;"><li>Dr. Zhao Liang, University of São Paulo, Brasil.</li><li>Dr. Marco Alvarez, Utah State University, Estados Unidos.</li><li>Dr. Diego Aracena Pizarro, University of Tarapacá, Chile</li><li>Dr. Guillermo Lafuente, University of La Pampa, Argentina.</li><li>Dr. Enrique Luna Ramirez, Technological Institute El Llano Aguascalientes, Mexico.</li><li>Dr. Mauricio Ochoa Echevarría, University of Boyacá, Colombia.</li><li>Dr. Alonso Inostrosa Psijas, Arturo Prat University, Iquique, Chile.</li><li>Dr. Claudio Meneses, Catholic University of the North, Antofagasta, Chile.</li><li>Dr. Brian Keith, Catholic University of the North, Antofagasta, Chile.</li><li>Dr. Ricardo Valdivia, University of Tarapacá, Arica, Chile.</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><a id="tittle_1" href="https://youtu.be/PlQf8uXiVL8" target="_blank">Primer Workshop de Informática Avanzada</a></strong></p> <video id='my-video' class='video-js responsive-video' controls preload='auto' width='340' height='191' poster='/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/hqdefault_1.jpg' data-setup='{}'> <source src='/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/easychair_1.mp4' type='video/mp4'> </video> <br><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><a id="tittle_2" href="https://youtu.be/5ARMiqXAsgA" target="_blank">Introducción a EasyChair para WIA - ¿Cómo presentar un documento?</a></strong></p> <video id='my-video' class='video-js responsive-video' controls preload='auto' width='340' height='191' poster='/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/hqdefault_2.jpg' data-setup='{}'> <source src='/2019/src/assets/media/cfp/easychair_2.mp4' type='video/mp4'> </video> <br><br><br><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Change language: <a href="/2019/call-for-papers?lang=en" style="color: black; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline;">English</a> - <a href="/2019/call-for-papers?lang=es" style="color: black; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline;">Spanish</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><footer id="main-footer" style="font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.15;"><div class="wrapper"> <article> <a href="<?= FOLDER_PATH . '/' ?>" id